PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779714673
OL,3,CVillages lose water supply on hottest
OL,4,Cday of the year
OL,6,FResident Amy Pitcher told ITV Meridian
OL,7,Fof her anger an frustration:
OL,9,F"Many of us are now without basic
OL,10,Fsanitation, including the ability to
OL,11,Fflush toilets.
OL,13,F"We also do not have the luxury of
OL,14,Fnearby supermarkets or easy access to
OL,15,Falternative supplies.
OL,17,F"We had the same issue in 2022, and
OL,18,Fwere without water for 6 days during
OL,19,Fthe hottest days of the year.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
